ON THE FRONT LINES.

217
00:16:31,708 --> 00:16:34,000
BUT AT LEAST I'D BE ABLE
TO HELP.

218
00:16:34,083 --> 00:16:37,291
- THE SPECIALIST OF EVERYTHING
WAS JUST HERE WITH NEWS.

219
00:16:37,375 --> 00:16:41,125
IT SEEMS
ONE OF OUTLAW'S MAIN POSTS

