00:17:01,791 --> 00:17:05,083
DAMAGE REPORTS
AND S.O.S. CALLS
HAVE BEEN COMING IN

228
00:17:05,166 --> 00:17:07,750
FROM OUTLAW POSTS
ALL OVER THE WORLD.

229
00:17:07,833 --> 00:17:11,083
- EXPLAINS WHY THE REPORTS
HAVE BEEN SUCH A MESS.

230
00:17:11,166 --> 00:17:13,416
YEAH, SO I'M GUESSING
THAT WASN'T EXACTLY

231
00:17:13,500 --> 00:17:15,750
WHAT YOU WANTED TO HEAR,
WAS IT?

232
00:17:15,833 --> 00:17:18,541
YOU STILL WANT TO WORK
FOR OUTLAW NOW?

233
00:17:33,833 --> 00:17:37,083
- IKE, WHAT'S UP?
- YOU'RE GOING, AREN'T YOU?

234
00:17:37,166 --> 00:17:38,333
- HUH?

235
00:17:38,416 --> 00:17:40,958
- OGATA'S GAME
THIS AFTERNOON.

236
00:17:41,041 --> 00:17:43,500
