- ( whistle blows )

239
00:17:55,291 --> 00:17:58,458
- TANAKA. 
- ( whistle blows )

240
00:18:00,958 --> 00:18:03,541
- ( grunts )
- ( whistle blows )

241
00:18:03,625 --> 00:18:05,791
- YEAH!

242
00:18:07,291 --> 00:18:09,541
( laughs )

243
00:18:13,208 --> 00:18:14,958
- ( whistle blows )

244
00:18:15,041 --> 00:18:16,875
- Girl: YOU GOT THIS, OGATA!

245
00:18:20,458 --> 00:18:21,916
- ( whistle blows )

