250
00:18:50,958 --> 00:18:53,541
- Alastor:
I KNEW YOU WEREN'T READY.

251
00:18:53,625 --> 00:18:57,625
I NEVER SHOULD HAVE AGREED
TO ADVANCE YOUR TRAINING LEVEL.

252
00:18:57,708 --> 00:18:59,583
- BUT I CAN FEEL IT.

253
00:18:59,666 --> 00:19:01,750
I CAN FEEL HER INTENT TO KILL.

254
00:19:01,833 --> 00:19:04,208
I'VE ALMOST GOT IT.

255
00:19:04,291 --> 00:19:06,791
- ALL RIGHT, YUJI.
THEN LET'S GO AGAIN.

256
00:19:11,791 --> 00:19:13,916
- ALL OF HER SWINGS ARE STRONG,

257
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:17,375
BUT ONE HAS MORE POWER
OF EXISTENCE BEHIND IT.

258
00:19:17,458 --> 00:19:22,125
SHE CONCENTRATES THAT POWER,
MAKING HER SWING DEADLIER.

259
00:19:22,208 --> 00:19:23,625
THIS IS IT!

260
00:19:31,750 --> 00:19:34,041
- DON'T LET YOUR GUARD DOWN.

261
00:19:34,125 --> 00:19:36,958
- NO JOKE.
LESSON LEARNED.

262
00:19:37,041 --> 00:19:40,083
- Alastor:
MMM.  I MUST SAY I'M IMPRESSED.

263
00:19:40,166 --> 00:19:43,666
I DIDN'T THINK
YOU'D BE ABLE TO DIFFERENTIATE
BETWEEN HER SWINGS.

264
00:19:43,750 --> 00:19:47,208
WELL DONE.  I THINK
WE SHOULD CALL IT A NIGHT.

265
00:19:47,291 --> 00:19:48,875
- NOT YET.

266
00:19:48,958 --> 00:19:52,250
