TO GET THE HANG OF IT.

267
00:19:52,333 --> 00:19:55,750
KEEP GOING, PLEASE.

268
00:19:55,833 --> 00:19:57,916
- YUJI.

269
00:20:01,916 --> 00:20:04,083
- Sato: 
THIS BETTER BE GOOD, MAN.
IT'S PRETTY LATE.

270
00:20:06,416 --> 00:20:10,541
- I WANTED TO APOLOGIZE.

271
00:20:10,625 --> 00:20:15,000
- YOU SERIOUSLY
DID NOT GET ME OUT OF BED
JUST FOR THIS, DID YOU?

272
00:20:15,083 --> 00:20:17,666
DAMN.
CHILLY OUT HERE.

273
00:20:17,750 --> 00:20:19,875
COME ON,
LET'S GO BACK TO MY PLACE

274
00:20:19,958 --> 00:20:23,541
AND TALK IT OUT THERE.
- I'M NOT GOING TO YOUR HOUSE.

275
00:20:23,625 --> 00:20:27,583
'CAUSE I DON'T
WANT TO SEE MARGERY.

276
00:20:27,666 --> 00:20:30,666
- SHE'S WORRIED ABOUT YOU.
