277
00:20:30,750 --> 00:20:33,708
SHE DOESN'T ACT LIKE IT,
BUT SHE DOES CARE.

278
00:20:33,791 --> 00:20:36,000
- YOU BELIEVE WHAT YOU WANT.

279
00:20:36,083 --> 00:20:37,500
BUT I DON'T EVER
WANT TO SEE HER AGAIN.

280
00:20:40,250 --> 00:20:44,041
