ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED TO HER
THAT DAY.

284
00:20:54,875 --> 00:20:57,208
I'M SCARRED FOR LIFE
'CAUSE OF IT.

285
00:20:58,875 --> 00:21:00,375
IN THE BEGINNING,

286
00:21:00,458 --> 00:21:02,791
