OF FOLLOWING MARGERY.

287
00:21:02,875 --> 00:21:06,041
BUT AFTER WHAT SHE DID,
I JUST CAN'T.

288
00:21:07,166 --> 00:21:09,125
- I UNDERSTAND.

289
00:21:09,208 --> 00:21:11,916
I'M GLAD YOU FOUND THE PATH

290
00:21:12,000 --> 00:21:13,791
THAT YOU WANT TO TAKE IN LIFE.

291
00:21:13,875 --> 00:21:16,208
- THANKS, SATO.

292
00:21:17,708 --> 00:21:20,166
( sobbing )

293
00:21:20,250 --> 00:21:24,583
- AW, CUT IT OUT.
BE A MAN, WOULD YA?

294
00:21:24,666 --> 00:21:28,500
IN ALL HONESTY, I'VE BEEN
HAVING SECOND THOUGHTS MYSELF.

295
00:21:28,583 --> 00:21:31,125
EVIDENTLY,
WORKING AT OUTLAW

296
00:21:31,208 --> 00:21:35,291
IS A LOT MORE DANGEROUS
THAN I THOUGHT IT'D BE.

297
00:21:35,375 --> 00:21:38,833
BUT, HEY,
I'VE ALREADY MADE MY DECISION.

298
00:21:38,916 --> 00:21:40,875
I'D FEEL
LIKE A COMPLETE LOSER

299
00:21:40,958 --> 00:21:43,875
IF I DIDN'T
FOLLOW THROUGH WITH IT.
YOU KNOW?

300
00:21:47,458 --> 00:21:50,708
- HERE, TAKE THIS.
GIVE IT BACK TO MARGERY.

301
00:22:08,416 --> 00:22:12,000
YOU CAN TELL HER
SHE WAS RIGHT.

302
00:22:12,083 --> 00:22:14,333
I AM THE TWERP
SHE THOUGHT I WAS.

303
00:22:14,416 --> 00:22:17,083
I'M JUST A GOOD FOR NOTHING,
WHINY COWARD.

304
00:22:17,166 --> 00:22:18,791
- NO, BUT YOU'RE BEING STUPID.

305
00:22:21,125 --> 00:22:25,500
TODAY'S THE DAY
YOU STOPPED BEING A COWARD.

